description: A few years ago, Jon Bon Jovi stopped performing due to a vocal cord injury. The Hulu docuseries Thank You, Goodnight offers a career retrospective, plus a view of his surgery and return to the stage.
title: 'I can only give the best': Bon Jovi on vocal surgery and the road to recovery

description: While some property owners try to turn a profit from the street artist's murals, others have carried the intense and costly responsibility of protecting them.
title: So your property has been 'Banksy-ed.' Now what?
